value.0: Corpses reanimated through necromancy, Zombies are mindless undead that shamble about, trying to satiate the dull ache of hunger in their decaying gut.
This corpse has suffered many grievous injuries, either before or after it was raised as undead. The resulting zombie is weak and halting.
